*.bak
*.backup
*~

# ==============================================================================
# Notes
# ==============================================================================
#
# IMPORTANT REMINDERS:
#
# 1. ALWAYS use vars.example.py as template
# 2. NEVER commit vars.py (contains customer data)
# 3. NEVER commit authentication files (.storage_*.json)
# 4. NEVER commit customer documents (PDFs, CSVs)
# 5. NEVER commit credentials or API keys
#
# To share configuration:
# - Update vars.example.py with new options
# - Document in SETUP_GUIDE.md
# - Never include actual customer names or paths
#
# ==============================================================================
